description:
Retrospective application for amendment to planning permission ref:  P010654 for: 

 a]   the removal of all spiral staircases to comply with      Lifetime Homes Standards; 

 b]   The change of the three bedroom ground floor flat G15      into a two  bedroom unit; 

 c]   the elimination of the maisonettes in the affordablke      housing element of the scheme; 

 d]   alterations to the form and shape of the roof and      details of dormer windows; 

 e]   the retention of part of the building at the rear left      hand side of the courtyard which was originally      approved for demolition, and the incorporation of these      areas into adjacent flats; 

 f]   the introduction of three sets of shafts with automatic      smoke vents throughout the building in accordance with      Building Control regulations. Applicants Plan Nos:  AR/A2/001-3,4B,5-8,9L,10I,11H,12G,                       13H,14J'15D'16F'17D-19D
